                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920523-23-off141 t17920523-23-crimeloc143"></join>. I lost this lead the 9th of last month; I missed it in the morning; it was taken from the cellar cieling.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17920523-23-person326">
                  SAMUEL
                   LUCK
